          <p>You have the right to make a complaint at any time to the Information Commissioner's Office (ICO), the UK supervisory authority for data protection issues (<a href="https://www.ico.org.uk" target="_blank">www.ico.org.uk</a>). We would, however, appreciate the chance to deal with your concerns before you approach the ICO so please contact us in the first instance. </p>
          <h3>CHANGES TO THE PRIVACY NOTICE AND YOUR DUTY TO INFORM US OF CHANGES</h3>
