          <p>Generally, we do not rely on consent as a legal basis for processing your personal data other than in relation to sending third party direct marketing communications to you via email. You have the right to withdraw consent to marketing at any time by <a href="https://www.tebex.io/contact/" target="_blank">contacting us</a>.</p>
